DISTRIBUTION. — Previously, this species had only been reported in the Upper Eocene/Lower Oligocene from the Rhine Graben in 
Germany
(
Schwarz & Griessemer 1994
; 
Schwarz 1997
). Ŋe occurrence of this species in Sant Boi de Lluçanès provides the first occurrence of this species in southern Europe (
Table 2
).

